  <DialogueData>k__BackingField:
    <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Bruxelles
    <CharacterPortrait>k__BackingField: {fileID: -1162642704207133085, guid: 10a8e30b7d8b77943ae72d49ed6c1f9b, type: 3}
    <DialogueLines>k__BackingField:
    - Let me present you your control interface.
    - On the upper right you can see how much time is left until the year ends...
    - ...how many emergencies you can fail to solve without losing...
    - ...and how much money you were allocated for the year. If you run out, you
      will also lose.
    - Underneath, you can see your units. You are allocated a certain amount for
      each year and will be able to buy more later.
